Day 30 of 30 Day Market Challenge

May 12, 2012 • grimmashauthor

Final Results:
<div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div>THE END!

And a record setting day!  And this gem happened today:

<div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div>Lesson:  Pay attention to your buy orders when you type them in.  This guy put an extra “1” in the hundreds digit, and I made about 70 mil off his mistake.  Woo!

Recap 

30 days ago I gave a fresh alt 5 million isk and just the basic trade skills.  Then I almost exclusively traded in stations, setting buy orders and flipping those to sell orders.  I started in Jita, moved to Amarr and then to Dodixie, and ended up back in Jita.  5 mil was turned into 1,461 million, or a 29,236% increase is value.  Here is the overall chart of the daily reports:
<div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">You can see the dips when I moved, as I cleared out stock before moving on.</div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">
</div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">My final Trade skills are:</div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;"></div><ul><li>Accounting 4</li><li>Broker Relations 4</li><li>Marketing 4</li><li>Procurement 4</li><li>Retail 4</li><li>Trade 4</li></ul><div>I didn’t even use all of those skills.</div>
<div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">
</div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">Hypothesis:  You can pay for a PLEX with a new character just by station trading.</div><div style="clear: both; text-align: left;">
